.SH ARCHITECTURE
.SS Script Structure
.RS
.EX
dotfiles (wrapper)
  ├── installed     → Query installed apps
  ├── config/stow   → Delegate to config
  ├── desktopmgr    → Delegate to desktopmgr
  ├── devenvmgr     → Delegate to devenvmgr
  ├── dfmgr         → Delegate to dfmgr (default)
  ├── dockermgr     → Delegate to dockermgr
  ├── fontmgr       → Delegate to fontmgr
  ├── hakmgr        → Delegate to hakmgr
  ├── iconmgr       → Delegate to iconmgr
  ├── lxcmgr        → Delegate to lxcmgr
  ├── passmgr       → Delegate to passmgr
  ├── pkmgr         → Delegate to pkmgr
  ├── systemmgr     → Delegate to systemmgr
  ├── thememgr      → Delegate to thememgr
  ├── virtmgr       → Delegate to virtmgr
  └── wallpapermgr  → Delegate to wallpapermgr
.EE
.RE
.SS Delegation Pattern
.RS
.EX
# Wrapper invocation
dotfiles {manager} {args}

# Translates to
{manager} {args}

# Example
dotfiles dfmgr install bash
# Becomes
dfmgr install bash
.EE
.RE
